---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
	description: "Explore the intersection of film and travel with AI as your guide.",
	title: "Movie Miles: AI-Powered Travel",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
  <h1 class="title mb-6">Movie Miles: AI-Powered Travel</h1>
  <div class="prose prose-citrus max-w-none">
    <p>
      Welcome to Movie Miles, where movies meet travel. Explore the intersection of film and travel, where stories come to life and every destination is a scene waiting to unfold.
    </p>
    <p>
      AI is our guide, the singular consciousness that helps us navigate the vast landscapes of the world. It's not about control, but about enhancing your travel experience, making every adventure unique and unforgettable.
    </p>
    <p>
      Here are some of the features that make Movie Miles unique:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-inside list-disc" role="list">
      <li>AI-powered travel recommendations</li>
      <li>Inspiration from movies and real-world destinations</li>
      <li>Personalized travel itineraries</li>
      <li>Integration with popular travel platforms</li>
      <li>Enhanced storytelling through film and travel</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Want to learn more or contribute to our project? Clone or fork our <a aria-label="github repository" class="citrus-link inline-block" href="https://github.com/yourusername/your-repo" rel="noreferrer" target="_blank">repo</a> if you like!
    </p>
  </div>
</PageLayout>